Package ohos.agp.components

Class DragEvent

  • java.lang.Object
    • ohos.agp.components.DragEvent

  • public class DragEvent
extends Object
    Defines attributes for drag events.

    Drag events are generated at various times during a drag and drop operation, that is, a user holds down an object and then drags it to another location.

    Since:
    1

      • isBroadcast

        public boolean isBroadcast​()
        Determines whether a drag event is being broadcasted.

        A drag event is considered being broadcasted if any of the following actions occur: DRAG_BEGIN, DRAG_MOVE, and DRAG_FINISH.

        Returns:
        Returns true if the drag event is being broadcasted; returns false otherwise.
